rows.label: tlk42350162_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Esasa tried to go to Iyasaki many
times now, but each time always
fail somehow.

rows.label: tlk42350162_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Like foot slip and fall into Cloud Sea,
and have to swim all way back up...

rows.label: tlk42350162_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Or spotted by Fleet Moramora and
almost eaten whole...

rows.label: tlk42350162_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Luckily, Esasa manage to prize open
mouth and escape. Esasa too high up
on food chain to become lunch!
